    "Thus, they are passing the responsibility to the next generation and to new AI developments.",
    "Consequently, the experts are not overly concerned about negative future scenarios.",
    "Although with this approach they also stated that they and their generation are not the only ones responsible for future AI in ICM, their optimistic interpretations and visions make them aware of their role as technology ambassadors.",
    "Thus, the experts in this study are fulfilling their role of being trust mediators (Bodo 2021).",
    "Recalling one of the key messages of the experts, AI is both media and an entity/actor."
